<div class="page-about pt-nav">

  {%- comment -%} ── 1. HERO ── {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="about-hero">
    {%- if section.settings.hero_image != blank -%}
      <img
        src="{{ section.settings.hero_image | image_url: width: 2400 }}"
        alt="MAMMOTH — Our Story"
        class="about-hero__img"
        loading="eager"
      >
    {%- else -%}
      <div class="about-hero__placeholder">[ Photo: Wide lifestyle shot — product detail or brand visual ]</div>
    {%- endif -%}
    <div class="about-hero__overlay">
      <span class="about-eyebrow">Built to endure</span>
      <h1 class="about-hero__title">Our Story</h1>
      <p class="about-hero__sub">Built to last. Built for the long run.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} ── 2. THE ORIGIN ── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-section about-section--white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-split">
        <div class="about-split__text">
          <span class="about-eyebrow about-eyebrow--dark">The idea</span>
          <h2 class="about-heading">A Mammoth Wasn't<br>Just Big</h2>
          <p class="about-body">It was built to endure. Through ice ages, across continents, through conditions that wiped out everything else. That's the energy behind MAMMOTH.</p>
          <p class="about-body">We started with a simple observation: most online stores feel disposable. Generic layouts, random products, zero personality. Cheap checkout experiences, thin product pages, and the quiet sense that nobody on the other end actually cares whether the thing shows up working.</p>
          <p class="about-body">We wanted to build something different. A store that actually feels like a brand — a place where every product is curated, every detail is intentional, and every customer interaction builds trust.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-split__media">
          {%- if section.settings.photo_patricio != blank -%}
            <img
              src="{{ section.settings.photo_patricio | image_url: width: 900 }}"
              alt="MAMMOTH — The idea"
              class="about-split__img"
              loading="lazy"
            >
            <p class="about-caption">Built to endure.</p>
          {%- else -%}
            <div class="about-photo-placeholder">
              <span>📷 Photo: Brand visual, lifestyle,<br>or hero product shot</span>
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} ── 3. STATS BAR — our values ── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-stats">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-stats__grid">
        <div class="about-stat">
          <span class="about-stat__num">01</span>
          <span class="about-stat__label">Strength</span>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stat about-stat--divider">
          <span class="about-stat__num">02</span>
          <span class="about-stat__label">Endurance</span>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stat about-stat--divider">
          <span class="about-stat__num">03</span>
          <span class="about-stat__label">Trust</span>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stat about-stat--divider">
          <span class="about-stat__num">04</span>
          <span class="about-stat__label">Vitality</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} ── 4. WHAT WE STAND FOR ── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-section about-section--beige">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-split about-split--reverse">
        <div class="about-split__media">
          {%- if section.settings.photo_tannery != blank -%}
            <img
              src="{{ section.settings.photo_tannery | image_url: width: 900 }}"
              alt="MAMMOTH — What we stand for"
              class="about-split__img"
              loading="lazy"
            >
            <p class="about-caption">Real value. No junk.</p>
          {%- else -%}
            <div class="about-photo-placeholder">
              <span>📷 Photo: Lifestyle, product in use,<br>or brand moment</span>
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
        <div class="about-split__text">
          <span class="about-eyebrow about-eyebrow--dark">What we stand for</span>
          <h2 class="about-heading">Strength Over Hype.<br>Substance Over Noise.</h2>
          <p class="about-body"><strong>Strength</strong> — we don't list junk. If a product can't hold up to our own testing, it doesn't make the catalog. Real value, priced honestly.</p>
          <p class="about-body"><strong>Endurance</strong> — we think in years, not weeks. That goes for the products we pick, the brand we're building, and the relationship we want with every person who orders.</p>
          <blockquote class="about-quote">
            "If it's not built to last, it doesn't belong here."
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} ── 5. HOW WE CURATE ── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-section about-section--white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-split">
        <div class="about-split__text">
          <span class="about-eyebrow about-eyebrow--dark">How we curate</span>
          <h2 class="about-heading">Every Product,<br>On Purpose.</h2>
          <p class="about-body">We don't chase trends and we don't stock everything. Each product in the MAMMOTH catalog earns its spot through a simple filter: does this actually make someone's day better?</p>
          <p class="about-body">We test before we list. We read the reviews. We run the numbers. If something sounds great on paper but falls apart in real use, it's out — no matter how good the margin looks.</p>
          <p class="about-body">What's left is a small, intentional collection of wellness-leaning goods built to earn a permanent spot in your day-to-day.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-split__media">
          {%- if section.settings.photo_sebastian != blank -%}
            <img
              src="{{ section.settings.photo_sebastian | image_url: width: 900 }}"
              alt="MAMMOTH — How we curate"
              class="about-split__img"
              loading="lazy"
            >
            <p class="about-caption">Curated, not stocked.</p>
          {%- else -%}
            <div class="about-photo-placeholder">
              <span>📷 Photo: Product flat lay,<br>detail shot, or workspace</span>
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} ── 6. WHO WE'RE FOR — dark section ── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-section about-section--dark">
    <div class="container about-truth">
      <span class="about-eyebrow">Who we're for</span>
      <h2 class="about-heading about-heading--light">Built for People Who<br>Care About the Details</h2>
      <p class="about-body about-body--light">The health-conscious. The quietly ambitious. People who read the label, compare the specs, and don't mind paying a little more for something that works properly the first time.</p>

      <div class="about-truth__grid">
        <div class="about-truth__card">
          <h3>Strength</h3>
          <p>Real value. No junk. Products that hold up in daily use, not just in the unboxing video.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-truth__card about-truth__card--highlight">
          <h3>Endurance</h3>
          <p>Long-run thinking. We'd rather ship fewer products and stand behind each one than flood the catalog with filler.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-truth__card">
          <h3>Trust &amp; Vitality</h3>
          <p>Clean design, honest copy, fast support. Goods that lean into wellness, energy, and everyday performance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="about-truth__kicker">Confident but not arrogant.<br>Clean but not cold.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} ── 7. HOW WE OPERATE ── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-section about-section--beige">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-split about-split--reverse">
        <div class="about-split__media">
          {%- if section.settings.photo_leather != blank -%}
            <img
              src="{{ section.settings.photo_leather | image_url: width: 900 }}"
              alt="MAMMOTH — How we operate"
              class="about-split__img"
              loading="lazy"
            >
            <p class="about-caption">Fast, clean, honest.</p>
          {%- else -%}
            <div class="about-photo-placeholder">
              <span>📷 Photo: Packaging, shipping,<br>or behind-the-scenes detail</span>
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
        <div class="about-split__text">
          <span class="about-eyebrow about-eyebrow--dark">How we operate</span>
          <h2 class="about-heading">Free US Shipping.<br>Straightforward Returns.</h2>
          <p class="about-body"><strong>Free shipping</strong> on every US order — no minimums, no games. Orders ship within 1–3 business days and typically arrive in 5–7.</p>
          <p class="about-body"><strong>30-day returns</strong> on unused items. If something arrives damaged or isn't what you expected, we fix it. One email, one reply, no runaround.</p>
          <p class="about-body"><strong>Real support</strong>. A person reads every message that comes into <a href="mailto:support@mammothstore.com">support@mammothstore.com</a>, usually within 24 hours on business days. If we made a mistake, we own it and make it right.</p>
          <p class="about-body">That's the whole model: good products, clean experience, honest service. Nothing more complicated than that.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} ── 8. CLOSING ── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-closing">
    {%- if section.settings.photo_closing != blank -%}
      <img
        src="{{ section.settings.photo_closing | image_url: width: 2400 }}"
        alt="MAMMOTH — Built to endure"
        class="about-closing__img"
        loading="lazy"
      >
    {%- else -%}
      <div class="about-closing__placeholder">[ Photo: Wide brand visual — lifestyle, product, or landscape ]</div>
    {%- endif -%}
    <div class="about-closing__overlay">
      <p class="about-closing__tagline">Built to endure. Built to last.</p>
      <p class="about-closing__body">MAMMOTH is a small team obsessed with getting the details right. The products, the packaging, the emails, the post-purchase experience — all of it. We're building the kind of store we'd want to buy from.</p>
      <p class="about-closing__sig">— The MAMMOTH Team</p>
      <a href="/collections/all" class="btn about-closing__btn">Shop the Collection</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</div>

<style>
/* ── About page base ── */
.page-about { color: var(--color-text); }

/* Hero */
.about-hero {
  position: relative;
  height: 40vh;
  min-height: 280px;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.about-hero__img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  object-position: center;
}
.about-hero__placeholder {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background: #2a2a2a;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  text-align: center;
}
.about-hero__overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 2rem;
}
.about-hero__title {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6rem);
  color: #fff;
  margin: 0.5rem 0;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  font-weight: 400;
}
.about-hero__sub {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
  margin: 0;
  font-style: italic;
}

/* Eyebrow label */
.about-eyebrow {
  display: block;
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.about-eyebrow--dark {
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
}

/* Sections */
.about-section { padding: 5rem 0; }
.about-section--white { background: #fff; }
.about-section--beige { background: #f5f0ea; }
.about-section--dark { background: #111; color: #fff; }

/* Split layout */
.about-split {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 4rem;
  align-items: center;
  max-width: 1100px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.about-split--reverse { direction: rtl; }
.about-split--reverse > * { direction: ltr; }

/* Text */
.about-heading {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.2;
  margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
}
.about-heading--light { color: #fff; }
.about-body {
  font-size: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.85;
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}
.about-body--light { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); }
.about-quote {
  border-left: 3px solid var(--color-text);
  margin: 2rem 0 0;
  padding-left: 1.25rem;
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: var(--color-text);
}

/* Photo */
.about-split__img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 520px;
  object-fit: cover;
  display: block;
}
.about-photo-placeholder {
  width: 100%;
  height: 520px;
  background: #e8e0d6;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  text-align: center;
  color: #999;
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
  border: 2px dashed #ccc;
}
.about-caption {
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
  margin-top: 0.75rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

/* Stats bar */
.about-stats {
  background: #1a1a1a;
  padding: 3rem 0;
}
.about-stats__grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  text-align: center;
}
.about-stat { padding: 1rem 2rem; }
.about-stat--divider { border-left: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); }
.about-stat__num {
  display: block;
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  color: #fff;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}
.about-stat__label {
  display: block;
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  margin-top: 0.4rem;
}

/* Truth section */
.about-truth { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
.about-truth__grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  margin: 3rem 0;
  text-align: left;
}
.about-truth__card {
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  padding: 2rem;
  border-radius: 2px;
}
.about-truth__card h3 {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.about-truth__card p {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  line-height: 1.75;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  margin: 0;
}
.about-truth__card--highlight {
  border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
}
.about-truth__card--highlight h3 { color: #fff; }
.about-truth__card--highlight p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); }
.about-truth__kicker {
  font-size: 1.15rem;
  font-style: italic;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin: 0;
}

/* Closing */
.about-closing {
  position: relative;
  min-height: 600px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}
.about-closing__img {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
}
.about-closing__placeholder {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: #1a1a1a;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
  font-size: 0.875rem;
}
.about-closing__overlay {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
  padding: 4rem 3rem;
  text-align: center;
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.about-closing__tagline {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
  color: #fff;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
}
.about-closing__body {
  font-size: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.about-closing__sig {
  font-style: italic;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
.about-closing__btn {
  background: #fff;
  color: #111;
  border-color: #fff;
}
.about-closing__btn:hover {
  background: transparent;
  color: #fff;
}

/* ── Mobile ── */
@media (max-width: 767px) {
  .about-split {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }
  .about-split--reverse { direction: ltr; }
  .about-split__img,
  .about-photo-placeholder { height: 320px; }
  .about-stats__grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
  }
  .about-stat--divider:nth-child(3) { border-left: none; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); }
  .about-stat--divider:nth-child(4) { border-left: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); }
  .about-truth__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .about-closing__overlay { padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem; }
}
</style>

